      "comment": "NOVA'S FERN (2) finds it hard to break through. Has been in the money the last five starts, the latest when third (34.96) at Angle Park. Form at the trip sound including three wins. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card last start despite being beaten. Expected to feature. MEPUNGA INFRARED (4) returned a better run last time, finishing in the money (30.04) at this track behind Duran Nirvana in a Grade 5. Got back and turned spotting a start but found the line impressively. Solid beginner who can clear the tricky draw. Expected to feature. MOONLIGHT RIVER (6) is not to be discarded.",
